title: Patty Duke Music Collection
description:
This is a comprehensive collection that includes every one of Patty Duke's recorded songs (in MP3 format). Also included is Patty Duke singing in many music photo albums and music videos from movies, TV variety shows, and The Patty Duke TV Show. Patty can be seen dancing in some of these music videos. Lastly, famous theme music is here from The Patty Duke Show and from two of Patty's movies (in various audio and video formats).
